<SP>
<SPEAKER>Ld. M.</SPEAKER>
<P>They what a devil&mdash;</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lovel.</SPEAKER>
<P>Plea&s;e to read on, my Lord. It cannot be <HI>her</HI> letter, if it does not make you admire her more and more as you read. Cou&s;in Charlotte, Cou&s;in Patty, pray at|tend &mdash;Read on, my Lord.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Mi&s;s Charlotte.</SPEAKER>
<P>Amazing fortitude!</P>
